thread.title: WSJ Survey: Most Economists Expect Next Fed Rate Rise in March

author: Harriet Torry
title: WSJ Survey: Most Economists Expect Next Fed Rate Rise in March
text:
Most economists polled by The Wall Street Journal expected the Federal Reserve will raise short-term interest rates in March and again in June.
Nearly 93% of business and academic economists surveyed this month predicted the Fedâ€™s first rate increase of 2018 will come at its March 20-21 policy gathering.
